		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">kyuusaku wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Did Nintendo provide a development manual?</div>
<br />
<br />Nope. We were sent one by our first publisher, Taxan (Magician), it was 99% Japanese. We spent a day with two Japanese girls (studying English I think) at a local university and they helped us decipher some of it. The rest we figured out by trial-and-error.
<br />
<br /><img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

